{"id":101044,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/中国最可悲之处：不承认也不接受教训/","date":"2010-08-27T17:13:38Z","modified":"2010-08-27T17:13:38Z","title":"中国最可悲之处：不承认也不接受教训","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，甘肃舟曲县遭到泥石流袭击，整个县城被毁，老百姓生命财产损失惨重，为此全国举哀；但</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>日</span><span>，前年四川汶川地震的中心映秀镇，又遭遇特大泥石流；专家估映秀泥石流的规模远超舟曲，幸运的是，当地人汲取了舟曲的教训，才没有重复多人被淹埋的惨剧。不过，刚建成的新家园再次毁于一旦。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年达沃斯论坛开始流行起来的一个新词：新常态。看来，大规模的救灾，已经成为中国的一种新常态。这不仅因为遭人为破坏的自然环境已十分脆弱，在日益增多的极端气候袭击下，不可避免地发生更多大灾，而且中国的救灾体制显然存在非常严重的弊端。</span></p>\n<p><span>甘肃舟曲发生的特大泥石流灾害至少造成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1245</span><span>人死亡，同时还有近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>百多人失踪（生 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><strong><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p></span></span></strong><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p>“